{"id":602048,"date":[{"year":1980,"month":10,"day":1}],"page":"3","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"笔会","column":"","genre":"","count":"250","ytitle":"","mtitle":"日出","ftitle":"","authors":["季涤尘"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"季涤尘"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当东方泛着玫瑰红的曙色，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海天相连处，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却是灰蒙蒙的一片；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是日出的时分未到，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还是云雾遮住了太阳的脸?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千万双眼睛注视着地平线，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有人用望远镜仔细观察，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有人将照相机捧在胸前；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大家都在等待着，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"等待那壮丽的一瞬间。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"终于，一个淡红色的球体"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"隐隐出现在"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轻纱般的云层后面；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一会儿，纱幕徐徐下落，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太阳的英姿霍然呈现。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他绯红的双颊艳如牡丹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他闪光的圆脸灿如黄金，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他冉冉上升，照耀人间；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他将亿万条金线，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"撒向蓝海和绿原。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在日出的一瞬间，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我想到前进中的祖国——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"瑰丽、伟大、威严；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它如同一轮红日，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向世界射出不灭的光焰。"}]}